Name: Log Entry 1
EntryCode: Enum of Assert | Deassert | values from table 42-1 and 42-2.  Really only for SEL
SensorType: For SEL.  Table 42-3 from IPMI Spec, same as in Metrics objects.
Number: EntityInstance from IPMI spec for SEL, count of events for Event, OEM Specific for OEM,
Message: Message for Event, Description for SEL, OEM depends
MessageID: Base.1.0.Success type for Event, EventData for SEL, OEM depends
